column4: saying Moscow's annexation of Crimea made them determined to reduce dependence on Russian oil and gas."

column1: {"headline": "U.N. Rights Investigator Accuses Israel of 'Ethnic Cleansing'"
column3: "lead_paragraph": "A U.N. human rights investigator accused Israel on Friday of \"ethnic cleansing\" in pushing Palestinians out of East Jerusalem and cast doubt that the Israeli government could accept a Palestinian state in the current climate."

column1: {"headline": "Obama to Meet With U.S. Tech Executives on Privacy
column4: "lead_paragraph": "Executives of several large U.S. Internet companies
column5: including Google Inc and Facebook Inc
column6: will meet with President Barack Obama on Friday to discuss changes to government surveillance programs."
